        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Mmmh...</P><P>What I understand is that it wipes Aggro List, putting you on top with low aggro factor. But still aggro. So basically if you Asystole a MOB (or something that really get them mad) + ST, your tank will easily taunt it off you.</P><P>It's also usefull to save your cleric or chanter in tight group situation with lot of adds that aggro them : take the beating, face the MOB and wait for your tank or FD.</P><P><img src="http://metacarpes.free.fr/images/preso/Pitz_portrait.jpg" border=0><BR>Pitzitmovaart Shadowgrigri :: 45 Necro :: Tholuxe Paells :: Metacarpes Member<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
